    <title>1.搭建个人博客教程</title>
    <link href="http://example.com/2022/12/07/%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA%E4%B8%AA%E4%BA%BA%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E6%95%99%E7%A8%8B/"/>
    <id>http://example.com/2022/12/07/%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA%E4%B8%AA%E4%BA%BA%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E6%95%99%E7%A8%8B/</id>
    <published>2022-12-07T03:27:28.000Z</published>
    <updated>2022-12-07T03:35:34.658Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h4 id="一、环境要求"><a href="#一、环境要求" class="headerlink" title="一、环境要求"></a>一、环境要求</h4><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">1. Node.js：</span><br><span class="line">    一个让JavaScript成为PHP、Python、Perl、Ruby等服务端语言平起平坐的      脚本语言</span><br><span class="line">    安装教程：https://www.cnblogs.com/liuqiyun/p/8133904.html</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">2. Git：</span><br><span class="line">    一个开源的分布式版本控制系统，可以有效、高速地处理从很小到非常大的项目版本管理</span><br><span class="line">    安装教程：https://www.cnblogs.com/xueweisuoyong/p/11914045.html</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h4 id="二、检查软件是否安装成功"><a href="#二、检查软件是否安装成功" class="headerlink" title="二、检查软件是否安装成功"></a>二、检查软件是否安装成功</h4><ol><li>按“Win”+“R”，输入“cmd”，使用如下命令检查是否安装成功</li></ol><img src="../images/搭建个人博客教程/1670383790384.png" alt="1670383790384" style="zoom:67%;" /><ol start="2"><li>在cmd界面使用命令“npm install hexo-cli -g”安装hexo的命令行界面（因为搭建所需要用到Hexo）</li></ol><img src="../images/搭建个人博客教程/1670383814095.png" alt="1670383814095" style="zoom:80%;" /><ol start="3"><li>在cmd界面使用命令“hexo -v”检查hexo是否安装成功</li></ol><img src="../images/搭建个人博客教程/1670383830708.png" alt="1670383830708" style="zoom:67%;" /><h4 id="三、Github账号注册"><a href="#三、Github账号注册" class="headerlink" title="三、Github账号注册"></a>三、Github账号注册</h4><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">账号注册网址教程：https://www.bilibili.com/read/cv5107169</span><br><span class="line">github网址：www.github.com</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h4 id="四、创建Github仓库"><a href="#四、创建Github仓库" class="headerlink" title="四、创建Github仓库"></a>四、创建Github仓库</h4><p><img src="/../images/%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA%E4%B8%AA%E4%BA%BA%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E6%95%99%E7%A8%8B/1670383887541.png" alt="1670383887541"></p><p><img src="/../images/%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA%E4%B8%AA%E4%BA%BA%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E6%95%99%E7%A8%8B/1670383890184.png" alt="1670383890184"></p><p><img src="/../images/%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA%E4%B8%AA%E4%BA%BA%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E6%95%99%E7%A8%8B/1670383893624.png" alt="1670383893624"></p><h4 id="五、生成SSH-Key与将Github与本地进行绑定"><a href="#五、生成SSH-Key与将Github与本地进行绑定" class="headerlink" title="五、生成SSH Key与将Github与本地进行绑定"></a>五、生成SSH Key与将Github与本地进行绑定</h4><ol><li>随便在电脑的某个路径目录下（PS:我这里是D:&#x2F;blog&#x2F;myblogs)右击空白处，选择“Github Bash Here”</li></ol><p><img src="/../images/%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA%E4%B8%AA%E4%BA%BA%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E6%95%99%E7%A8%8B/1670383924463.png" alt="1670383924463"></p><ol start="2"><li>输入命令” ssh-keygen -t rsa -C ‘你的邮件地址’ ”（PS:邮件地址必须是你当时注册Github所使用的地址）</li></ol><p><img src="/../images/%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA%E4%B8%AA%E4%BA%BA%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E6%95%99%E7%A8%8B/1670383935640.png" alt="1670383935640"></p><ol start="3"><li>命令输入完成后，连续敲4次回车，如图所示</li></ol><p><img src="/../images/%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA%E4%B8%AA%E4%BA%BA%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E6%95%99%E7%A8%8B/1670383943748.png" alt="1670383943748"></p><ol start="4"><li>在C:&#x2F;users&#x2F;用户名目录下有一个近期生成的.ssh文件夹（PS:用户名因人而异，我这里是whg）</li></ol><p><img src="/../images/%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA%E4%B8%AA%E4%BA%BA%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E6%95%99%E7%A8%8B/1670383951552.png" alt="1670383951552"></p><ol start="5"><li>通过notepad++（也可以通过记事本）打开“id rsa.pub”文件，全选复制里面的内容，回到github，在个人中心找到”setting“，找到“SSH and GPG keys”</li></ol><p><img src="/../images/%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA%E4%B8%AA%E4%BA%BA%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E6%95%99%E7%A8%8B/1670383958336.png" alt="1670383958336"></p><p><img src="/../images/%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA%E4%B8%AA%E4%BA%BA%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E6%95%99%E7%A8%8B/1670383960614.png" alt="1670383960614"></p><p><img src="/../images/%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA%E4%B8%AA%E4%BA%BA%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E6%95%99%E7%A8%8B/1670383963634.png" alt="1670383963634"></p><p><img src="/../images/%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA%E4%B8%AA%E4%BA%BA%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E6%95%99%E7%A8%8B/1670383966357.png" alt="1670383966357"></p><p><img src="/../images/%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA%E4%B8%AA%E4%BA%BA%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E6%95%99%E7%A8%8B/1670383968884.png" alt="1670383968884"></p><p><img src="/../images/%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA%E4%B8%AA%E4%BA%BA%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E6%95%99%E7%A8%8B/1670383971023.png" alt="1670383971023"></p><p><img src="/../images/%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA%E4%B8%AA%E4%BA%BA%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E6%95%99%E7%A8%8B/1670383973534.png" alt="1670383973534"></p><ol start="6"><li>通过命令“ssh -T <a href="mailto:&#x67;&#x69;&#x74;&#64;&#103;&#105;&#116;&#104;&#117;&#x62;&#46;&#x63;&#111;&#x6d;">&#x67;&#x69;&#x74;&#64;&#103;&#105;&#116;&#104;&#117;&#x62;&#46;&#x63;&#111;&#x6d;</a>“测试是否绑定成功</li></ol><p><img src="/../images/%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA%E4%B8%AA%E4%BA%BA%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E6%95%99%E7%A8%8B/1670383983153.png" alt="1670383983153"></p><h4 id="六、本地生成博客内容"><a href="#六、本地生成博客内容" class="headerlink" title="六、本地生成博客内容"></a>六、本地生成博客内容</h4><ol><li>输入命令“hexo init”初始化hexo，如果报错则多尝试几次命令或者以管理员方式运行git bash，因为github是国外网站，相对于来说速度较慢</li></ol><p><img src="/../images/%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA%E4%B8%AA%E4%BA%BA%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E6%95%99%E7%A8%8B/1670384000673.png" alt="1670384000673"></p><ol start="2"><li>输入命令“hexo s”在本地搭建hexo界面，通过提示的网站查询界面，按Ctrl+c会停止hexo服务</li></ol><p><img src="/../images/%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA%E4%B8%AA%E4%BA%BA%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E6%95%99%E7%A8%8B/1670384008762.png" alt="1670384008762"></p><p><img src="/../images/%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA%E4%B8%AA%E4%BA%BA%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E6%95%99%E7%A8%8B/1670384011639.png" alt="1670384011639"></p><h4 id="七、发布博客到互联网"><a href="#七、发布博客到互联网" class="headerlink" title="七、发布博客到互联网"></a>七、发布博客到互联网</h4><ol><li>之前在Git Bash中输入“hexo init”命令时相应的路径会生成一系列的文件，在这些文件中找到config.yml</li></ol><p><img src="/../images/%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA%E4%B8%AA%E4%BA%BA%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E6%95%99%E7%A8%8B/1670384030672.png" alt="1670384030672"></p><ol start="2"><li>以记事本或者notepad++以及其他软件打开，然后如图所示</li></ol><p><img src="/../images/%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA%E4%B8%AA%E4%BA%BA%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E6%95%99%E7%A8%8B/1670384039137.png" alt="1670384039137"></p><p><img src="/../images/%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA%E4%B8%AA%E4%BA%BA%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E6%95%99%E7%A8%8B/1670384041587.png" alt="1670384041587"></p><ol start="3"><li>（PS：根据上图所示，仓库的地址在Github里面找）</li></ol><p><img src="/../images/%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA%E4%B8%AA%E4%BA%BA%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E6%95%99%E7%A8%8B/1670384050779.png" alt="1670384050779"></p><p><img src="/../images/%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA%E4%B8%AA%E4%BA%BA%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E6%95%99%E7%A8%8B/1670384052794.png" alt="1670384052794"></p><ol start="4"><li>在Git Bash中输入命令“npm install hexo-deployer-git –save”</li></ol><p><img src="/../images/%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA%E4%B8%AA%E4%BA%BA%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E6%95%99%E7%A8%8B/1670384062228.png" alt="1670384062228"></p><p><img src="/../images/%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA%E4%B8%AA%E4%BA%BA%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E6%95%99%E7%A8%8B/1670384064351.png" alt="1670384064351"></p><ol start="5"><li>输入用户名，用户名是github的用户名字</li></ol><p><img src="/../images/%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA%E4%B8%AA%E4%BA%BA%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E6%95%99%E7%A8%8B/1670384072231.png" alt="1670384072231"></p><p><img src="/../images/%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA%E4%B8%AA%E4%BA%BA%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E6%95%99%E7%A8%8B/1670384074363.png" alt="1670384074363"></p><p><img src="/../images/%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA%E4%B8%AA%E4%BA%BA%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E6%95%99%E7%A8%8B/1670384076803.png" alt="1670384076803"></p><p><img src="/../images/%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA%E4%B8%AA%E4%BA%BA%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E6%95%99%E7%A8%8B/1670384079037.png"></p><p><img src="/../images/%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA%E4%B8%AA%E4%BA%BA%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E6%95%99%E7%A8%8B/1670384111654.png" alt="1670384111654"></p><p><img src="/../images/%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA%E4%B8%AA%E4%BA%BA%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E6%95%99%E7%A8%8B/1670384115214.png" alt="1670384115214"></p><p><img src="/../images/%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA%E4%B8%AA%E4%BA%BA%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E6%95%99%E7%A8%8B/1670384118108.png" alt="1670384118108"></p><p><img src="/../images/%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA%E4%B8%AA%E4%BA%BA%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E6%95%99%E7%A8%8B/1670384120905.png" alt="1670384120905"></p><ol start="6"><li>输入网址，大功告成</li></ol><p><img src="/../images/%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA%E4%B8%AA%E4%BA%BA%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E6%95%99%E7%A8%8B/1670384132599.png" alt="1670384132599"></p>]]></content>
    
    
      
      
